Package towersim.ground

Classes representing entities on the ground of an airport including terminals and gates.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AirplaneTerminal
    Represents an airport terminal that is designed to accommodate airplanes.
    Gate
    Represents an aircraft gate with facilities for a single aircraft to be parked.
    HelicopterTerminal
    Represents an airport terminal that is designed to accommodate helicopters.
    Terminal
    Represents an airport terminal building, containing several aircraft gates.
